sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant ServiceAuth
    participant AuthDB

    User            ->>  ServiceAuth    :   HTTP POST http://service-auth/api/v1/users/register \nCreateUserRequest
    ServiceAuth     ->>  AuthDB         :   check email and username
    alt email or username available in db
        AuthDB      -->> ServiceAuth    :   AuthEntity
        ServiceAuth -->> User           :   HTTP 409 Conflict
    else Not Found
        AuthDB          -->> ServiceAuth    :   not found
        ServiceAuth     ->>  ServiceAuth    :   hash password (BCrypt)
        ServiceAuth     ->>  AuthDB         :   save AuthEntity
        AuthDB          -->> ServiceAuth    :   saved AuthEntity
        ServiceAuth     -->> User           :   HTTP 200 OK CreateUserResponse
    end